Aerotaur/Nightlight/Windlord:::


Altought Aerotaur let go Nightlight towards Starstomp and Trinity, he 
was uneasy. Birdbot and Parpetron might be around and just Primus 
could know what might happen.


Windlord when he saw that Aerotaur was Worried, he aske to his friend 
what was going on.

"I shouldn't have let Nightlight goes alone where TRinity and 
Starstomp are" answered Aerotaur.

"You should better go with her" replied Windlord "I can handle the 
situation here "

Aerotaur nodded and he ran towards the exit, in the same moment that  
Nightlight was leaving the basse.
